\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Grateful):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I appreciate your willingness to meet Maggie. I know she\u8217\'92s not supposed to get too close to my inner circle, but I couldn\u8217\'92t free my schedule up in time to pick her up before the play we\u8217\'92re seeing tonight....\u8221\'94 }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Evan paused and admitted the deeper truth) }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Plus, I wanted you to meet her.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Curious, inquisitive):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s okay. I am quite curious to meet her. I know you still have a few weeks to make a decision, but have you decided to start your year together with her?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Informative response):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Not officially. I want to make sure that a relationship is something that she wants. And I wanted her to meet you first.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 :}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You don\u8217\'92t need my approval.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Sincere):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I know, but it will be difficult to move forward without Maggie meeting you. I\u8217\'92m not worried, though. You\u8217\'92ll love her. She\u8217\'92s a hard-working, down-to-earth girl, and we get along great!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Encouraged By the effect Maggie seems to have had on Evan):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I must say you have been in a great mood this week. How many dates have you had so far?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Informative response):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Four altogether. We had our first date at the fall festival and three afternoon dates this week.\u8221\'94 }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Evan\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92s facial expression lights up)}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93She\u8217\'92s been teaching me how to cook.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Intrigued, helpful):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So I\u8217\'92ve heard. Trish told me about your surprise for Maggie. Do you need any help setting up?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 :}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Nope. I got it all covered.\u8221\'94}
