\par\pard\plain \tx0\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 [ I want to introduce Liz}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 \loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8217\'92}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 s fertility problems through a narrative, as opposed to dialogue. It felt inorganic for Evan and Liz to discuss details in this setting, and repeating it here doesn}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 \loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8217\'92}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 t make much sense because they both already know what they know. So here}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 \loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8217\'92}{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 s what you need to know to insert her fertility backstory into the scene.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 - Liz had always dreamed of conceiving and birthing a child naturally. For the longest time, she was steadfast against IVF procedures and adoption.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 - Liz had multiple miscarriages, her last one a year ago.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 - Unable to get pregnant in over a year, and now 31, Liz has reconsidered her options.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 - She initially visualized having two children before her 30th birthday. She feels time is running out, and after several long talks with Joe and her friend and OB/GYN, Alicia, Liz relented and decided to do the IVF procedure.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 - This procedure is scheduled for the next day. This is the subject of the next stretch of dialogue when Evan asks her how she feels about the procedure.}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4  ]}
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Wanting to check in on Liz):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Enough about me. How are you feeling about your procedure tomorrow?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Her facial expressions show nervousness more than excitement):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Nervous and excited at the same time.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Supportive, anxious to help):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t know much about the procedure, but if you need anything at all, let me know.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Liz}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Downplaying her own fears):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I appreciate that. But there is no need to worry. It\u8217\'92s an outpatient procedure, and Alicia is a pro.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 [ Their conversation is interrupted by a text from Maggie on Evans\loch\af4\hich\af4\dbch\af4\uc1\u8217\'92 phone.]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 Evan}{\f2\fs26\b1\i0  }{\f4\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 (Exuberant):}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s Maggie, she\u8217\'92ll be here soon. I\u8217\'92ve got to go finish setting up her surprise.\u8221\'94}
